@node "Statistics" "DazWall - Statistics"

                               @{b}Statistics@{ub}

DazWall has a VERY extended statistics-window. To get there, just press 'S'
on the prompt. A window will appear, looking something like this:

     _____ __ _ _ ______________________________________ ______ _ __ _____
   __)    _ __ __\\_____________________________________\\______ __ _    (__
_¦_\                                                                       /_¦_
 ¦        Named Tags.........................................:      27       ¦
 ¦        Anonymous Tags.....................................:      14       ¦
 ¦        Number of Removed Lines............................:       4       ¦
 ¦                                                             ------- +     ¦
 ¦        Total Tags.........................................:      45       ¦
 ¦                                                                           ¦
 ¦                                                                           ¦
 ¦         .--------------------------------------------------------.        ¦
 ¦         ¦                Top 10 Taggers on DazWall               ¦        ¦
 ¦         ¦--------------------------------------------------------¦        ¦
 ¦         ¦ 1. 21   -  HiFi             6. 1    -  DELITE          ¦        ¦
 ¦         ¦ 2. 10   -  RADAVI           7. 1    -  PRODiGY         ¦        ¦
 ¦         ¦ 3. 3    -  Dazzler          8. 1    -  Cloak           ¦        ¦
 ¦         ¦ 4. 2    -  Protonic         9. 1    -  WildCard        ¦        ¦
 ¦         ¦ 5. 2    -  StRaWhEaD       10.                         ¦        ¦
 ¦         `--------------------------------------------------------'        ¦
 ¦          __ ___________________________________________________ _         ¦
 ¦         (_//__________________________________________________//_)        ¦
 ¦                                                                           ¦
_¦__                       Press any key to continue...                    __¦_
 ¦ /_     _ __ _______ ______________________________________ __ __ _     _\ ¦
     )____ __ _ _____//____________________________________//_ _ __ _____(

I think this is quite self-explaining. The top-10-list is created using the
doors:dazwall/user.log, so don't delete this file if you want to keep your
top-10-list intact :)

The statistics will all be set to '0' if you clear the wall using the Clear
Wall-option in the online-configger.

                             @{" Back to Main " link "Main" 0}

@endnode

